"```sql\nSELECT z.city, z.state\nFROM member m\nJOIN major ma ON m.link_to_major = ma.major_id\nJOIN zip_code z ON m.zip = z.zip_code\nWHERE ma.department = 'Electrical and Computer Engineering Department'\n  AND m.position = 'Member';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the city and state of members who are enrolled under the \"Electrical and Computer Engineering Department\" and have the position of \"Member.\" It joins the `member` table with the `major` table to filter by department and with the `zip_code` table to retrieve the city and state information."